{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0129Cnyf2UZxAZnGUZtujjHK","type":"tool_result","content":"commit 7c4b213a99f7914f71af4356ab30a13f455500ec\nAuthor: Lee Gonzales <lee.gonzales@gmail.com>\nDate:   Sat Jan 24 12:57:13 2026 -0700\n\n    fix(parser): Normalize image paths and allow extra content sections\n    \n    - Add normalizeImagePath() to ensure consistent images/ prefix\n    - Normalize image paths from both slides table and content sections\n    - Make content section validation lenient: skip unknown slugs instead of error\n    - Allows appendix sections without requiring slides table entry\n    \n    Fixes: PresentationKit-lzz (mixed image path formats)\n    Fixes: PresentationKit-m1o (appendix slides validation error)\n    \n    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n src/parsers/talk-track.ts | 48 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-----\n 1 file changed, 43 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01Hv4DasBDFoVNnhH6QmfxmU","session_id":"fae97709-6dbb-4c53-abde-6088a81b1e30","uuid":"fb8dc08d-6280-4385-9b57-8d57fe9d1f06"}
